<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B5104029003">
<title>
DTC Confirmation Procedure
</title>
<attention1>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Perform road test in a place where there is no traffic to prevent an accident.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Road test should be performed with two persons, a driver and a tester, on a level road.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Warm up engine to normal operating temperature.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Drive vehicle at more than 50 km/h (31 mile/h) in “D” range for 5 min.
</ptxt>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B5104029004">
<title>
DTC Troubleshooting
</title>
<diag type = "test" id = "AENAP70B5104029005">
<testgroup id = "AENAP70B5104029006">
<question>
Was “A/T Control System Check” performed?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 2.
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to 
<intxref refid = "AENAP70B5104001">A/T Control System Check</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENAP70B5104029007">
<title>
Input shaft speed sensor circuit check
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Set ignition “OFF” and disconnect connectors from input shaft speed sensor and TCM.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Check for proper terminal connection to input shaft speed sensor and TCM connectors.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
If connections are OK, check that each input shaft speed sensor circuit (A1, A2) is as follows.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Wiring harness resistance of each input shaft speed sensor circuit is less than 1 Ω.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Insulation resistance of each input shaft speed sensor circuit is infinity between input shaft speed sensor connector and ground.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Insulation resistance of wire harness is infinity between input shaft speed sensor (+) circuit terminal and (–) circuit terminal at input shaft speed sensor connector.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Circuit voltage of each input shaft speed sensor circuit is approx. 0 V with ignition “ON”.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</test1>
<question>
Are they in good condition?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 3.
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Repair or replace defective wire harness.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENAP70B5104029008">
<title>
Input shaft speed sensor check
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Check input shaft speed sensor. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70B5106021"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</test1>
<question>
Is it in good condition?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 4.
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Replace input shaft speed sensor. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70B5106020"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENAP70B5104029009">
<title>
Input shaft speed sensor visual check
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Remove input shaft speed sensor. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70B5106020"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Check input shaft speed sensor visually as follows.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
No damage
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
No foreign material attached
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Correct installation
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
<testfigure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B510020.swf" width = "90.000mm" height = "27.270mm" ver = "01" gw = "101" gh = "61"/>
</testfigure>
</test1>
<question>
Are they in good condition?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<paragroup>
<ptxt>
Check for intermittent trouble. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70B0006002"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
If OK, substitute a known-good TCM and recheck DTC. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70B5106030"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</paragroup>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Clean, repair or replace input shaft speed sensor.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
</diag>
